  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc2\u0d9c\u0dda \u2019\u2019\u0d9a\u0db4\u0dd4\u0da7\u0dd4\u2019\u2019\u0d9a\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0da9\u0dba\u0db1\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u2019\u2019\u0d9a\u0db4\u0dd4\u0da7\u0dd4\u2019\u2019\u0d8b\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A \"crow\" answer from Diana to Harsha's \"crow\" story",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The appointed MP Diana Gamage said in the Parliament that Samagi Jana Balawega has also laid eggs in the crow's nest.",
        "Mrs. Diana Gamage said that MP Harsha de Silva told a story about the eggs being laid in the crow's nest in the Parliament and said that she laughed when she heard that story.",
        "Mrs. Diana Gamage said that what Samagi Jana Balawega has done is to come to \"my nest\" and lay eggs, so don't attack your leader by saying that you should not lay eggs in the crow's nest.",
        "Samagi Jana Balawega's Colombo District Councilor Dr. Harsha De Silva while addressing the Parliament said yesterday that \"Ranil's economic policy is like a chick in a nest\"."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Diana to Harsha's",
          "label": "ORG"
